1. CONTROLS:
 - move laft: rotate teephone left;
 - move right: rotate telephone right;
 - jump/land: touch screen. 

2. POINTS:
 - apple: + 5 points;
 - pear: + 10points;
 - frozen apple: health - 5;
 - frozen pear: health - 10;
 - collision with ice: - 1 life;
 - collision with snowball: - 1 life.
